<figureCitation box="[927,1040,379,401]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="8.[175,214,892,911]" captionTargetBox="[153,1169,194,876]" captionTargetId="figure-288@8.[153,1169,194,876]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="Figs. 14–17. Druantia aeterna, new species. 14) Anterior view; 15) Dorsal view; 16) Lateral view; 17) Ventral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5335066" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5335066/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="217">Figs. 16–17</figureCitation>
